# metafid
## Codal

![PyPI - Python Version](https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/codalpy)
![PyPI - Version](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/codalpy)
![PyPI - Downloads](https://img.shields.io/pypi/dm/codalpy?logoColor=blue&color=blue)
